Fairly nice read, the story is satisfying and doesnt leave me with too many questions. My one big question is why, why does she want to be a slut? Maybe it was answered in part one, but who knows, other than that, a solid work.
Fapability: 7.5/10, very nice artwork with an incredibly beautiful mc
Story:7/10, it's a nice spin on the prostitution route and is innovative, could be better with some more context, but its fine, does tell the reader about the future in the last page.
Dialogue: 7/10, I do enjoy my nympho girls but this dialogue does its job in setting the mood as well as explaining motives and goals of the characters
Overall enjoyability: 7.5/10, the story only goes to compliment the dialogue and the artwork does wonders for the enjoyability. Not a bad read at all and doesn't overstay its welcome. I personally approve this to be recommended to upper low tier to mid tier hentai enthusiasts.
